                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.60 Manchuria/4–3046: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul General at Mukden</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clubb</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-04-30T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >April 30, 1946—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>12. Dept would appreciate such detailed info as may be available regarding
                    Russian seizure of Jap industrial enterprises Manchuria, especially Anshan.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
